
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Building and Installing clazzy
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

To install clazzy, ensure that you have a recent version of g++ (or another C++
compiler with C++11 support), cmake, and flex(++).

In Linux or similar environemnts, run the following commands as root:

    cmake .
    make

Alternatively, if you have makepkg available, you can simple use build/PKGBUILD
to make and install clazzy:

    cd build/
    makepkg

